HEADWORD: Liroconite
<hw>Li*roc"o*nite</hw> <pr>(l⟦isl⟧*r⟦ocr⟧k"⟦osl⟧*n⟦imac⟧t)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>leiro`s</grk> pale + <grk>koni`a</grk>
